{"type": "article", "id": 1342, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2014-07-03T09:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 1464, "name": "圣马丁"}, {"id": 1465, "name": "Loft"}, {"id": 1466, "name": "Hermès"}, {"id": 1467, "name": "懒人神器"}, {"id": 1468, "name": "智能斑马线"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155156WdFKt4sVnYzSU8x6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t1.  The Saint Martins Lofts by <a href=\"http://www.bostockandpollitt.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bostock and Pollitt </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t圣马丁 Loft，地处伦敦查令街，建造在中央圣马丁艺术学院教学楼旧址上的，原建筑历史可以追溯到 1939 年，公寓分为四层，有 10 间公寓和 2 间阁楼出售。圣马丁学院自是为公寓增添了艺术气息（和噱头），当然公寓内外设计都很不俗，住在这里还可以享受伦敦 SOHO 区的生活也是一大卖点。户型面积在1250 平方英尺到 3000 平方英尺，价格则 200 万英镑起，已经卖出去不少套，手快有手慢无<a href=\"http://www.saintmartinslofts.com/enquiries/%E9%A2%84%E8%B4%AD\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里预购</a>，如果买不到，还是那句话，看看人家装修也不错。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155144oEdH6ncLl54wkTFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155145CXcRS03IoBZ1jU8h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061551459lghFcodQbBMUP14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155145dwPAW7oNh5yjlRUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155146ygwr6iGnLMv5JW9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155147ARIFMaylguLxsGof.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t2.  Hermès barcelona store window by <a href=\"http://www.zimandzou.fr/70282/gallery\" target=\"_blank\">Zim &amp; Zou</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t来自法国 Zim &amp; Zou 工作室为爱马仕巴塞罗那一家店铺设计的橱窗——狐狸窝，除了那只狐狸是皮制的，其他所有装置均为纸质，纯手工制作。鲜亮的橘色是爱马仕的标志色，其中展出的爱马仕领带、丝巾、瓷器仿佛都体现着狐狸主人的品味，似乎可以让人感受到它的日常生活。好玩、耐看还带着艺术气息的橱窗，令人过目不忘。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155147e9DBZFbfP6d8YXOl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155148DBIRmxOT4d6WJ1pS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155149Zl8GJQphEsrHquSP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155149THAZ2rCESpWDMPi6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155150UBX4n6DsGkbKrj3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155150DYROTN8FWm3uazHk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155151tfsol1LeyhKgxPXI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t3.  One Bowl by <a href=\"http://www.theonebowl.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Justin Herd </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t厌倦了煮个 pasta 还要又刷锅又刷碗的日子？懒人必备的神器来了，One Bowl 里可以完成加热、滤水、吃和储存四项功能，相当于锅、笊篱、碗和保鲜饭盒的集合体，除了节省碗柜里的储存空间，最大的好处还要数终于不用刷那么多锅碗瓢盆了，真是离好生活又近了一步！<a href=\"http://www.theonebowl.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155151hy09HCJIYfztMdON.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155152SZDRJxVIyk90swqj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155152puWLJQdEqfm7Nljr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155153mveKXkZLIVBh6n5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t4.  Food Huggers by <a href=\"http://foodhuggers.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Adrienne McNicholas and Michelle Ivankovic</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t通常切开的蔬菜水果最容易从切面开始腐坏，设计师于是设计出了蔬果盖子，接触蔬果的地方由硅胶制成，可以完全贴合蔬果的切面，大大降低蔬果腐坏的速度，减少浪费。不论从持家角度还是道德角度，这都是个好设计，<a href=\"http://foodhuggers.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155153tT8bnAizuDJWQ9VL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155154jZ2kqyP7UiOcHlhC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155154qASanRzt6v87ZjDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155154DneRUjZwfthuAYa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t5.  The Smart Crosswalk by<a href=\"http://chugi.ru/\" target=\"_blank\"> Alexey Chugunnikov </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t智能斑马线下面装有感应器和发光器，如果有行人踏上斑马线，它就会立即发出红光，让司机从视觉上感觉到前方有障碍物而减速行驶；在天色较暗的时候它还会自动发出白光，便于车辆和行人识别。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155155pkE3Y9bBXnVcjM4l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155155nWcr6FKRlP5t9dE8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155156kCMjEvSfqOHemTLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}